==English==
===Etymology===
From scientific {{L.}} ''[[Onchocerca]]'' (a genus of parasitic worms, from {{AGr.}} '''{{polytonic|[[ὄγκος]]}}''' ‘barb’ + '''{{polytonic|[[κέρκος]]}}''' ‘tail’) + ''[[-iasis]]''.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ɒŋkəsɜːˈkaɪəsɪs/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{medicine}} A disease caused by a [[worm]] of the genus ''Onchocerca'', especially as transmitted to humans by flies and often causing [[blindness]]; common in tropical Africa.

